title: ISic000546. I.Sicily inscription 000546
body:
Facsimile Images

------
[---]ẹṭ Q(uinti) ((·)) Fabi ((·)) Caesili ((·)) Titiani
[---]avo ((·)) Q(uinto) ((·)) Aquilio ((·)) Nigro
[--- p]ro ((·)) co(n)s(uli)
Si[cili]ae

Apparatus criticus

Text of CIL, based upon Auria; Auria: II at start of line.
4: Auria: SIM..AE

English translation

...[and] of Quintus Fabius Caesilius Titianus...for [his] uncle Quintus Aquilius Niger...proconsul...of Sicily
